//   Drill into a specific auth-fail pattern that delivered:
//   EmailEvents
//   | where Timestamp > ago(30d)
//   | where AuthenticationDetails has "fail" and DeliveryAction == "Delivered"
//   | project Timestamp, SenderFromAddress, Subject, AuthenticationDetails
